Quickstrike:




Quickstrike stepped to Black Arachnia's side and put his cobra hand 
gently on her shoulder. There was something about her that 
immediately told him that she was uneasy. 

She whispered to her, just in case she was still busy with the 
transmttion, "This bot here wants t' join." Mentioning about Cyber 
Claw. "She brought Rattrap wit' 'er in stasis lock. Ah put 'im in th' 
CR chamber.
